messages.text: Hey babe how are you today
OK.
These kids are exhausting
Aww
What happened
No one in my entire first period history class did their homework.
Oh
Maybe they were all exhausted or something?
From what? From being 17?
I dont know
I’m sorry. You’re right. The whole thing’s just hard, you know?
I know
Did you feel like this your first year as a teacher??
Oh ya totally. All the time.
Id just go easy on the kids
Theyre probably having a hard time too
I was thinking…
You wanna get drinks later?
It’d be nice to talk for real.
Face to face.
Oo I would love that too. But you know we cant
I dont want to mess things up
You’re right.
Can’t believe we’re not allowed to date colleagues.
I mean we’re all adults, right?
Haha I know so dumb
But its been real nice texting with you all the time
I know it’s been good for me too.
Good to have someone to talk to in this town.
God this town is so dumb I know
I saw you in the teacher lounge the other day
O ya???
I wanted to say something. To do something. You know?
:) :) :) I dont know what you mean
Tell me tell me tell me
Let me tell you over drinks
Ahh you know I cant!
You looked so good the other day
O ya??
Your butt looked really good in those pants today
Huh?
You have such a cute butt
Wait how do you know what I look like today?
Oh I saw you in the hallway earlier.
But you’re not in school today. I went by your room earlier and there’s a sub.
Oh
Karen?
Im sorry
What
Im so sorry Mr Haverson
Who is this??
HELLO WHO IS THIS??
Lindsey
Lindsey who??
Lindsey from first period history
what??
Lindsey this is serious. Why do you have Karen’s phone?
No Mr. Haverson you dont get it. Im so sorry.
Youre so cute. I thought maybe you knew it was me and you were still playing along
Playing along with what?
I got your number from that sheet you gave us the first day of class
Dont be mad! I just think your really really great.
And sorry about class today. Danny had a crazy party last night and a lot of us were out super late
Mr Haverson?
Lindsey this is really inappropriate.
Im sorry :(
I said a lot of things to you.
It was so nice
And those photos
LINDSEY you have to delete those photos!
Aww but you look so cute.
No Lindsey this isn’t okay
Even the one of you with your dog?
Jesus Christ
This whole time?
So you made up everything about Karen ignoring me
Ms. Waters didn’t know anything
But shes really pretty so I thought you would want to talk to her
She hasn’t been ignoring me. She doesn’t even know me!
Im so so so sorry
But I meant everthing I said
Your such a good teacher
Does anyone else know about this Lindsey?
No I never told anyone
OK. Meet me in my classroom after school. Okay?
NO Lindsey NOT like that. We need to talk about this.
:(( sorry
You can’t show anyone these
I wont tell anyone
My room. After school. Bring your phone.
